<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>观赏期</strong>：6-9月</p>
<p><strong>扶摇直上</strong></p>
<p><strong>向日葵海</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200923/e21c2811d46343f3b15a108edb76ad25.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
